Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止倒退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前為止 沒什麼危險的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 破廢鐵會將鯨烏賊全部消滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破廢鐵 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認棲息於該海域的希迪亞斯已全部殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 幹得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 把人形機器人全部開出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的寶物是我們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
